overview.en: USDT CLUB hopes to create a platform for everyone to have a deeper understanding of the blockchain market, and to further understand the blockchain investment, so as to make rational investment in the blockchain.
overview.zh: USDT CLUB希望打造一个平台，让大家对区块链市场有一个更深的了解，同时对区块链投资有更进一步的了解，从而对区块链进行理性投资。
